```markdown
"Will address in follow-up PR" is PROHIBITED unless:
- Issue requires external system access (infrastructure)
- Issue requires CS2 authority (contract modification)
- Issue is documented as BLOCKER and escalated immediately

Quality issues within agent authority MUST be fixed immediately.
```

