```

**THIS IS THE ROOT CAUSE**: governance-repo-administrator.agent.md hasn't been updated with YAML_VALIDATION_PROTOCOL.md (PR #682 from office-app). It's still using old `yamllint` command that validates entire .md files instead of frontmatter only.

